<span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size"><span class="bbc_u">¿Cómo cambiar el tamaño del avatar en el index?</span></span></strong></span><br /><br />Buscar el archivo <em>index.template.php</em> en la ubicación <em>/Themes/tu-theme/index.template.php</em><br /><br />En el archivo, buscar algo como ésto:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// If the user is logged in, display stuff like their name, new messages, etc.<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if ($context&#91;&#039;user&#039;]&#91;&#039;is_logged&#039;])<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if (!empty($context&#91;&#039;user&#039;]&#91;&#039;avatar&#039;]))<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo &#039;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;p class=&quot;avatar&quot;&gt;&#039;, $context&#91;&#039;user&#039;]&#91;&#039;avatar&#039;]&#91;&#039;image&#039;], &#039;&lt;/p&gt;&#039;;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo &#039;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;ul class=&quot;reset&quot;&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li class=&quot;greeting&quot;&gt;&#039;, $txt&#91;&#039;hello_member_ndt&#039;], &#039; &lt;span&gt;&#039;, $context&#91;&#039;user&#039;]&#91;&#039;name&#039;], &#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;&#039;, $scripturl, &#039;?action=unread&quot;&gt;&#039;, $txt&#91;&#039;unread_since_visit&#039;], &#039;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;&#039;, $scripturl, &#039;?action=unreadreplies&quot;&gt;&#039;, $txt&#91;&#039;show_unread_replies&#039;], &#039;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#039;;<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// Is the forum in maintenance mode?<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if ($context&#91;&#039;in_maintenance&#039;] &amp;&amp; $context&#91;&#039;user&#039;]&#91;&#039;is_admin&#039;])<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo &#039;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li class=&quot;notice&quot;&gt;&#039;, $txt&#91;&#039;maintain_mode_on&#039;], &#039;&lt;/li&gt;&#039;;</code><br />Y modificar el código correspondiente del avatar, en la forma como se muestra:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if (!empty($context&#91;&#039;user&#039;]&#91;&#039;avatar&#039;]))<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo &#039;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;p class=&quot;avatar&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;&#039;, $context&#91;&#039;user&#039;]&#91;&#039;avatar&#039;]&#91;&#039;href&#039;], &#039;&quot; style=&quot;width: 100px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#039;;</code><br />Donde &quot; style=&quot;width: 100px;&quot; controla el tamaño del Avatar mostrado en el index.<br /><br />Aquí hay un poco de info al respecto:<br /><a href="http://www.simplemachines.org/community/index.php?topic=451866.0" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.simplemachines.org/community/index.php?topic=451866.0</a><br />
